<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.mich;10;601" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PMich10,601</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Διογένης Δημητρίωι χαί-

    <lb n="2"/>ρειν. γίνωσκε ἡμᾶς κε-

    <lb n="3"/>κωλῦσθαι ἐργάζεσθαι 

    <lb n="4"/>ὑπὸ Πτολεμαίου τοῦ Με-

    <lb n="5"/>νεσθέως καὶ Πτολεμαίου 

    <lb n="6"/>τοῦ Ἡρακλείδου τῶν λογευ-

    <lb n="7"/>όντων τὴν ἐπιγραφὴν 

    <lb n="8"/>τὰς δύο <num value="2"/> δραχμὰς τῶι με-

    <lb n="9"/>τρητῇ, καὶ φάσκειν αὐτοὺ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> 

    <lb n="10"/>παραγράφεσθαί σε κεραμίων 

    <lb n="11"/>ἑβδομήκοντα <num value="70"/> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="140">ρμ</num> καὶ κε-

    <lb n="12"/>νοῦ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="10">ι</num>, ὥστ᾽ εἶναι <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="150">ρν</num>. 

    <lb n="13"/>σὺ οὖν καλῶς <choice><corr>ποιήσεις</corr><sic>ποεισεις</sic></choice> φροντί-

    <lb n="14"/>σας ὡς οὐ περισπασθησόμε-

    <lb n="15"/>θα. καὶ ὑπὲρ <choice><corr>κλημάτων</corr><sic>κλημα<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">το</del>ατων</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="16"/>οὐχ ὑπομενεῖ <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ἐὰν μ</del> <add place="supralinear">κατ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ά</unclear></add>γειν 

    <lb n="17"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὁ</supplied> καταμήνιος, ἐὰν μὴ χα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>-

    <lb n="18"/>κοῦς λάβῃ. ἔρρωσο. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="19"/>σ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὺ</unclear> <choice><corr>ο<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ὖ</supplied>ν</corr><sic>ον</sic></choice> φρόντιζε ὡς δεθή-

    <lb n="20"/>σεται τὰ ξύλα <choice><corr>καὶ ἄν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> που 

    <lb n="21"/>ἀνενεχθῇ διασάφη-

    <lb n="22"/>σόν μοι. 

    <lb n="23"/>Δημητρίω<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date type="textDate">210 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BO 30, 1973, S. 240.</p></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">SB</title><biblScope type="volume">18</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">13861</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">2609</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0239</series>; <biblScope type="volume">18</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">13861</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0239;18;13861" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">P.Mich. X, Pl. VIII (Rekto)</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">ZPE 23, 1976, Tafel X c (Verso)</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">P.Mich. X 601</bibl></div><div n="meta.2609" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Kloppenborg, Tenants in the Vineyard (2006), S